<lyrics>[V1]
 1- (ʿly̱
 ạlṣlyb sẖuft ḥbyby wbạlậlạm mjrwḥ lạ̉jly
 sẖuft ṭryqy ạ̉kẖdẖt slạmy
 wbạlslạm qult ạ̹mlạ̉ qlby)2
 qrạr- sā̉lwạ ạlnạs mnyn
 slạmk qult mn ʿnd ạlmṣlwb
 lmạ ṣlybh ḍmn ly ḥyạty
 wbqyt kẖạly mn ạlʿywb
 ạlly mʿạya wbyqwly dmy
 ʿlyk dmy ʿlyk ḥrrk mn ạlkẖṭyẗ
 dmy ʿlyk dmy ʿlyk ḥrrk
 mn ạlʿbwdyẗ
 2
 - (ʿly̱ ạlṣlyb bdạ̉t ḥyạty wbạlṣlyb ʿrft rby
 lmạ ạlfạdy jh kẖd ậlạmy
 wtw̃bny wmạḥy dẖnby)2
 3
 - (ʿly̱ ạlṣlyb rby sẖfạny dm ạlṣlyb ṭh̃r ly qlby
 lmạ yswʿ ḍm̃d jrạḥy
 wbạlnʿmẗ bqyt mthñy)2
 4</lyrics>
<title>ʿly̱ ạlṣlyb</title>
